uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.store.disk

Interface IMatcher

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DCustomMatcher, IDirectMatcher, NDirectMatcher, NMatcher, ORConceptsMatcher, ORIndividualsMatcher, ORMatcher, OROntologyBasedMatcher, OTMatcher

    public interface IMatcher
    Provides mechanisms for storing and executing queries over representations of sets of instantiations of a MEKON Frames Model (FM).

    All of the instance-level frame/slot-network representations of instances and queries that are passed into the matcher methods will be "free-instance" copies of the originals (see IFreeCopier).
